name: Lieutenant Cecius
Lore: 'Former member of the Imperial infantry. Specializes in boarding and taking control of enemy ships. Native of Vogel 7. Hasn''t had a date in years.',
Text: 'Deploys free to any Executor site. Power +3 when participating in a Besieged battle. During your control phase, may use 1 Force to search your Reserve Deck, take one Besieged or Set For Stun into hand and reshuffle.',
